AD_TAB.NAME: Custody Details
AD_TAB.HQLWHERECLAUSE: e.id not in ( select e.escmMrequestCustody.id from escm_custody_transaction e join e.escmMaterialReqln as req where req.id=@Escm_Material_Reqln.id@ ) and ( ( e.id in ( select e.escmMrequestCustody.id from escm_custody_transaction e left join e.goodsShipmentLine as line left join line.shipmentReceipt as req where e.isProcessed='Y' and e.transactiontype='RE' and req.warehouse.id=@Escm_Material_Request.warehouse@ ) and (e.alertStatus='RET' )) or (e.id in (select e.id from Escm_Mrequest_Custody e where e.alertStatus='RET'))) and( e.id in ( select trans.escmMrequestCustody.id from escm_custody_transaction trans,EUT_HijiriDates hijiri where to_date(to_char(hijiri.gregorianDate,'yyyy-MM-dd'),'yyyy-MM-dd') =to_date(to_char(trans.transactionDate,'yyyy-MM-dd'),'yyyy-MM-dd') and ( (substr(hijiri.hijriDate, 1,4)||'-'||substr(hijiri.hijriDate, 5,2)||'-'|| substr(hijiri.hijriDate, 7,2)) <= @Escm_Material_Request.transactionDate@ ) and trans.isProcessed='Y' and trans.returnDate is null )) and e.product.id=@Escm_Material_Reqln.product@

AD_TAB.NAME: Return Custody Detail
AD_TAB.HQLWHERECLAUSE:
(e.escmMaterialReqln.id in ( select e.id from Escm_Material_Reqln e join e.escmMaterialRequest req where req.organization .id=@MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.organization@ and req.alertStatus='ESCM_TR' ) or (e.escmMaterialReqln.id is null )) and ((@MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.escmReceivingtype@='INR' and e.alertStatus='IU' and @MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.escmBtype@<>'MA' ) or (@MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.escmBtype@='MA' and e.alertStatus='MA' ))
and e.id not in ( select e.escmMrequestCustody.id from escm_custody_transaction e join e.goodsShipmentLine as line join line.shipmentReceipt as req where req.id=@MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.id@ ) and( e.id in ( select trans.escmMrequestCustody.id from escm_custody_transaction trans,EUT_HijiriDates hijiri where to_date(to_char(hijiri.gregorianDate,'yyyy-MM-dd'),'yyyy-MM-dd')=to_date(to_char(trans.transactionDate,'yyyy-MM-dd'),'yyyy-MM-dd') and ( (substr(hijiri.hijriDate, 1,4)||'-'||substr(hijiri.hijriDate, 5,2)||'-'|| substr(hijiri.hijriDate, 7,2)) <= @MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.movementDate@ ) and trans.isProcessed='Y' and trans.returnDate is null ) or (e.escmMaterialReqln.id is null ))
and(( e.beneficiaryType = @MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.escmBtype@ and e.beneficiaryIDName.id = @MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.escmBname@ and @MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.escmBtype@<>'MA') or( @MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.escmBtype@='MA' and e.beneficiaryType ='MA') or (e.beneficiaryType is null and e.beneficiaryIDName is null ))

AD_TAB.NAME: Site Material Issue Request
AD_TAB.HQLWHERECLAUSE: e.id in (select coalesce(a.id,'') as id from Escm_Material_Request a join a.eUTNextRole r join r.eutNextRoleLineList l where l.role.id=@#AD_Role_ID@ and a.alertStatus <>'DR')and ( e.issiteissuereq in ('Y') ) or (e.id in (select b.escmMaterialRequest.id from Escm_Materialrequest_Hist b where b.updatedBy.id =@AD_User_ID@ and b.role.id=@#AD_Role_ID@ ) and ( e.issiteissuereq in ('Y') )) or ( e.createdBy.id=@AD_User_ID@ and e.role.id = @#AD_Role_ID@ and ( e.issiteissuereq in ('Y') )) or (e.id in (select req.id from Escm_Material_Request req where Exists( select 1 from Eut_Docapp_Delegate dl join dl.eutDocappDelegatelnList dll where dll.userContact.id=@#AD_User_ID@ and dll.role.id = @#AD_Role_ID@ and dll.documentType='EUT_112' and now() between dl.fromDate and dl.date and dl.role.id in ( select li.role.id from Escm_Material_Request re join re.eUTNextRole rl join rl.eutNextRoleLineList li))) and ( e.issiteissuereq in ('Y') ))

AD_TAB.NAME: Add Lines
AD_TAB.HQLWHERECLAUSE:
(e.escmMaterialReqln.id in ( select e.id from Escm_Material_Reqln e join e.escmMaterialRequest req where req.organization .id=@MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.organization@ and req.alertStatus='ESCM_TR' ) or (e.escmMaterialReqln.id is null )) and ((@MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.escmReceivingtype@='LD' and e.alertStatus='IU' and @MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.escmBtype@<>'MA' ) or (@MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.escmBtype@='MA' and e.alertStatus='MA' ))
and e.id not in ( select e.escmMrequestCustody.id from escm_custody_transaction e join e.goodsShipmentLine as line join line.shipmentReceipt as req where req.id=@MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.id@ ) and (e.id in ( select trans.escmMrequestCustody.id from escm_custody_transaction trans,EUT_HijiriDates hijiri where to_date(to_char(hijiri.gregorianDate,'yyyy-MM-dd'),'yyyy-MM-dd')=to_date(to_char(trans.transactionDate,'yyyy-MM-dd'),'yyyy-MM-dd') and ( (substr(hijiri.hijriDate, 1,4)||'-'||substr(hijiri.hijriDate, 5,2)||'-'|| substr(hijiri.hijriDate, 7,2)) <= @MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.movementDate@ ) and trans.isProcessed='Y' and trans.returnDate is null )or (e.escmMaterialReqln.id is null ))
and(( e.beneficiaryType = @MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.escmBtype@ and e.beneficiaryIDName.id = @MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.escmBname@ and @MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.escmBtype@<>'MA') or( @MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.escmBtype@='MA' and e.beneficiaryType ='MA'))

AD_TAB.NAME: Partial Counting
AD_TAB.HQLWHERECLAUSE: e.id not in(select a.escmProductStockV from MaterialMgmtInventoryCountLine a where a.physInventory.id = @MaterialMgmtInventoryCount.id@) and (e.storageBin.id in (select a.id from Locator a where a.warehouse.id=@MaterialMgmtInventoryCount.warehouse@) or e.storageBin.id = null) and e.product.stocked=true

AD_TAB.NAME: Header
AD_TAB.HQLWHERECLAUSE: EM_Escm_Receivingtype='INR' and ( (e.id in (select coalesce(a.id,'') as id from MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut a join a.eutNextRole r join r.eutNextRoleLineList l where l.role.id=@#AD_Role_ID@ and a.escmDocstatus <>'DR')) or (e.id in (select b.goodsShipment.id from ESCM_Custodytransfer_Hist b where b.updatedBy.id =@AD_User_ID@ and b.role.id=@#AD_Role_ID@ )) or ( e.createdBy.id=@AD_User_ID@ and e.escmAdRole.id=@#AD_Role_ID@))

AD_TAB.NAME: Custody Add Line
AD_TAB.HQLWHERECLAUSE: e.beneficiaryType = @MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.escmBtype@ and e.beneficiaryIDName.id = @MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.escmBname@ and (e.alertStatus='IU') and e.id not in ( select e.escmMrequestCustody.id from escm_custody_transaction e join e.goodsShipmentLine as line join line.shipmentReceipt as req where req.id=@MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.id@ ) and (e.id in ( select e.escmMrequestCustody.id from escm_custody_transaction e where to_date(to_char(e.transactionDate,'YYYY-MM-DD'),'YYYY-MM-DD') <= to_date(@MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.escmRefDate@,'YYYY-MM-DD') and e.returnDate is null) or (e.escmMaterialReqln.id is null ))

AD_TAB.NAME: Custody Details
AD_TAB.HQLWHERECLAUSE:
(e.escmMaterialReqln.id in ( select e.id from Escm_Material_Reqln e join e.escmMaterialRequest req where req.organization .id=@MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.organization@ and req.alertStatus='ESCM_TR' ) or (e.escmMaterialReqln.id is null )) and (@MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.escmReceivingtype@='IRT' and e.alertStatus='RET') and e.id not in ( select e.escmMrequestCustody.id from escm_custody_transaction e join e.goodsShipmentLine as line join line.shipmentReceipt as req where req.id=@MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.id@ ) and ( e.id in ( select e.escmMrequestCustody.id from escm_custody_transaction e left join e.goodsShipmentLine as line left join line.shipmentReceipt as req
where e.isProcessed='Y' and e.transactiontype='RE' and req.warehouse.id=@MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.warehouse@ ) or (e.escmMaterialReqln.id is null )) and (e.id in ( select trans.escmMrequestCustody.id from escm_custody_transaction trans,EUT_HijiriDates hijiri where to_date(to_char(hijiri.gregorianDate,'yyyy-MM-dd'),'yyyy-MM-dd')=to_date(to_char(trans.transactionDate,'yyyy-MM-dd'),'yyyy-MM-dd') and ( (substr(hijiri.hijriDate, 1,4)||'-'||substr(hijiri.hijriDate, 5,2)||'-'|| substr(hijiri.hijriDate, 7,2)) <= @MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut.movementDate@ ) and trans.isProcessed='Y' and trans.returnDate is null) or (e.escmMaterialReqln.id is null ))

AD_TAB.NAME: Custody Transfer
AD_TAB.HQLWHERECLAUSE: e.escmIscustodyTransfer='Y' and ((( (select count(pd.id) from ADPreference pd where pd.propertyList='Y' and pd.property='ESCM_CTIsAdmin' and (pd.visibleAtClient.id=@#AD_Client_ID@ or pd.visibleAtOrganization.id=@#AD_Org_ID@ or pd.visibleAtRole.id=@#AD_Role_ID@ or pd.userContact.id=@#AD_User_ID@ or pd.window.id='D6F05B3A695E4D6BB357E1B6686E3D4D'))=0 and ( e.createdBy.id=@#AD_User_ID@ and e.escmAdRole.id = @#AD_Role_ID@ )) or ( (select count(pd.id) from ADPreference pd where pd.propertyList='Y' and pd.property='ESCM_CTIsAdmin' and (pd.visibleAtClient.id=@#AD_Client_ID@ or pd.visibleAtOrganization.id=@#AD_Org_ID@ or pd.visibleAtRole.id=@#AD_Role_ID@ or pd.userContact.id=@#AD_User_ID@ or pd.window.id='D6F05B3A695E4D6BB357E1B6686E3D4D'))=1 and 1=1 )) or( (e.id in (select coalesce(a.id,'') as id from MaterialMgmtShipmentInOut a join a.eutNextRole r join r.eutNextRoleLineList l where l.role.id=@#AD_Role_ID@ and l.userContact.id=@#AD_User_ID@ and a.escmDocstatus <>'DR')) or (e.id in (select b.goodsShipment.id from ESCM_Custodytransfer_Hist b where b.updatedBy.id =@AD_User_ID@ and b.role.id=@#AD_Role_ID@ )) ))

AD_TAB.NAME: Material Issue Request
AD_TAB.HQLWHERECLAUSE: (e.id in (select coalesce(a.id,'') as id from Escm_Material_Request a join a.eUTNextRole r join r.eutNextRoleLineList l where l.role.id=@#AD_Role_ID@ and a.alertStatus <>'DR') and ( e.issiteissuereq not in ('Y') or e.issiteissuereq is null ) or (e.id in (select b.escmMaterialRequest.id from Escm_Materialrequest_Hist b where b.updatedBy.id =@AD_User_ID@ and b.role.id=@#AD_Role_ID@ ) and ( e.issiteissuereq not in ('Y') or e.issiteissuereq is null )) or ( e.createdBy.id=@AD_User_ID@ and e.role.id = @#AD_Role_ID@ and ( e.issiteissuereq not in ('Y') or e.issiteissuereq is null )) or (e.id in (select req.id from Escm_Material_Request req where Exists( select 1 from Eut_Docapp_Delegate dl join dl.eutDocappDelegatelnList dll where dll.userContact.id=@#AD_User_ID@ and dll.role.id = @#AD_Role_ID@ and dll.documentType='EUT_112' and now() between dl.fromDate and dl.date and dl.role.id in ( select li.role.id from Escm_Material_Request re join re.eUTNextRole rl join rl.eutNextRoleLineList li))) and ( e.issiteissuereq not in ('Y') or e.issiteissuereq is null ))) and e.beneficiaryType in (select ref.searchKey from EUT_ListAccess lsacc join lsacc.listReference as ref where lsacc.window.id='D8BA0A87790B4B67A86A8DF714525736' and lsacc.role.id=@AD_Role_Id@ and lsacc.active=true)
